http://maps.hslan.de

It's a rush-map and funny to play with bots. Original map was made by Cyber-Net / Lasse G. N. and called 'cs_warehouse_c-n1' but had a bug with buyzones. Our clan loves to play the map and it's in our mapcycle for some months now. 

Because Lasse's page was down and he's not reachable I decided to rebuild it with some changes.
